queries.query: SELECT      c.c_name,      o.o_orderdate,      o.o_totalprice,      l.l_extendedprice,      l.l_discount FROM      tpch1g.customer c JOIN      tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN      tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE      l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' ORDER BY      o.o_orderdate, l.l_extendedprice DESC;

SELECT   l.l_orderkey,   l.l_partkey,   l.l_suppkey,   l.l_extendedprice,   l.l_discount,   o.o_orderdate FROM   tpch1g.lineitem l JOIN   tpch1g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey WHERE   c.c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM tpch1g.nation WHERE n_name = 'GERMANY') ORDER BY   l.l_extendedprice DESC, o.o_orderdate;

SELECT   l.l_orderkey,   l.l_partkey,   l.l_suppkey,   l.l_extendedprice,   l.l_discount,   o.o_orderdate,   p.p_name FROM   tpch1g.lineitem l JOIN   tpch1g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey WHERE   c.c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM tpch1g.nation WHERE n_name = 'GERMANY') ORDER BY   l.l_extendedprice DESC, o.o_orderdate;

SELECT   l.l_orderkey,   l.l_partkey,   l.l_suppkey,   l.l_extendedprice,   l.l_discount,   o.o_orderdate,   p.p_name,   s.s_name FROM   tpch1g.lineitem l JOIN   tpch1g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN   tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN   tpch1g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey JOIN   tpch1g.supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey WHERE   c.c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM tpch1g.nation WHERE n_name = 'GERMANY') ORDER BY   l.l_extendedprice DESC, o.o_orderdate;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment FROM tpch1g.lineitem;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment FROM tpch1g.lineitem;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment FROM tpch1g.lineitem;
